works.description: At its Premiere Collector’s Firearms Auction (May 20-22, 2011), Rock Island Auction Company will offer over 2,700 lots, including antique and collectible firearms manufactured by Colt, Winchester, Holland & Holland and more. It’s the first of the three Premiere auctions the Illinois-based auction house holds every year. Leading the lots is a U.S. marked and inspected Colt 2nd Model Dragoon Revolver manufactured in 1851.
